    "Id": "MichelangeloSlaves7",
    "Steps": [
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "Well, since I am a clever owl, I have one idea!",
                "fr": "Eh bien, comme je suis une chouette maline, j'ai une idée !",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "We know from sketches that they were intended to go on the bottom of the monument",
                "fr": "Nous savons grâce à des croquis qu'ils étaient destinés à être placés au bas du monument",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Image",
            "Parameters": {
                "Display": "FullScreenWidth",
                "Width": 738,
                "Height": 600,
                "Source": "Web",
                "Path": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dgy6y4npc/image/upload/v1536836026/10slaves_tombsketch.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "So, perhaps they are sinners being punished?",
                "fr": "Donc peut-être qu'ils étaient des pécheurs qui devaient être punis ?",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Pause",
            "Parameters": {
                "Mode": "Wait",
                "ms": 1000
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "Or maybe heretics?",
                "fr": "Ou peut-être des hérétiques ?",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Pause",
            "Parameters": {
                "Mode": "Wait",
                "ms": 1000
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "They could be representations of provinces conquered by the papacy?",
                "fr": "Ils pourraients être des représentations des provinces conquises par la papauté",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "You can decide for yourself!",
                "fr": "Tu peux décider par toi-même !",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            }
        }
    ],
    "Commands": [
        {
            "Type": "Node",
            "Id": "MichelangeloSlaves7Mysterious",
            "ElementValue": "1",
            "CommandLabel": {
                "en": "How mysterious!",
                "fr": "Comme c'est mystérieux !",
                "es": "",
                "cn": ""
            },
            "Steps": [
                {
                    "Type": "Text",
                    "Label": {
                        "en": "Anyway… they were actually left off the final version of the mausoleum, supposedly due to spacing issues!",
                        "fr": "Quoiqu'il en soit, ils ont été finalement enlevés de la version finale du mausolée, apparemment à cause de problèmes de place !",
                        "es": "",
                        "cn": ""
                    }
                },
                {
                    "Type": "Text",
                    "Label": {
                        "en": "So Michelangelo gave them to his friend, Roberto Strozzi!",
                        "fr": "Donc Michel-Ange les donna à son ami, Roberto Strozzi !",
                        "es": "",
                        "cn": ""
                    }
                },
                {
                    "Type": "Text",
                    "Label": {
                        "en": "And now, the Louvre has them!",
                        "fr": "Et maintenant, elles sont exposées au Louvre !",
                        "es": "",
                        "cn": ""
                    }
                }
            ],
